[b]Emission model:[/b] The adaptive emission controller targets 2,625,000 QUG/year in Era 0 (the first 4 years), regardless of block production rate. Faster blocks produce smaller rewards. Slower blocks produce larger rewards. The daily target is constant. First halving occurs 4 years after genesis.

[b]Fair launch.[/b] No premine. No ICO. No VC allocation. VDF mining levels the playing field.


