[b]Use the Wallet:[/b] Visit [url=https://quillon.xyz]quillon.xyz[/url] for the full web wallet with DEX, token deployment, AI chat, and more.

[b]Important:[/b] If you ran mainnet2026.1, simply download the new binary. It automatically uses a fresh data directory (data-mainnet2026.2). Your old data remains untouched but is no longer used. Old binaries cannot connect to the new network.


